(1443, 32, 1, 'The hyperthyroid patient complains of fatigue, but still cannot get to sleep. The nurse suggests:', 'Bedtime rituals like a warm bath, reading, listening to music cue the body for sleep. Naps during the day may make night time sleep difficult, exercising and drinking caffeine filled drinks are stimulating and should be avoided by the person with insomnia.', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 15:56:19', '2021-01-21 15:56:19'),
