(1462, 32, 1, 'The patient, seeking additional information about her diagnosis of hypothyroidism, asks if this condition has been present since infancy. The nurse responds:', 'If not treated early, hypothyroidism during infancy causes permanent retardation called cretinism.', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:17:27', '2021-01-21 16:17:27'),
(1463, 32, 1, 'An older patient wondered why the doctor has decreased her daily dose of thyroid hormone. The nurse’s best response would be that the decreased dose is because:', 'Older patients have slower drug metabolism, and so the drug stays in their system. All patients receiving hormone replacement need to be evaluated periodically.', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:17:56', '2021-01-21 16:17:56'),
(1464, 32, 1, 'Your neighbor complains of being cold all the time. In addition, she looks depressed and very weary. You suspect that she may have a thyroid deficiency. All the following are nursing diagnoses for hypothyroidism except:', 'Because the metabolism has slowed down, there is a decreased need for calories.', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:19:28', '2021-01-21 16:19:28'),
(1465, 32, 1, 'To address the nursing diagnosis Risk for impaired skin integrity related to dry skin, in the patient with hypothyroidism, the nurse would:', 'Her skin requires lubrication in order to prevent breakdown. Frequent bathing and anti-histamines dry skin. Exercise does little for skin perfusion.', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:21:22', '2021-01-21 16:21:22'),
(1466, 30, 1, 'PNP members conduct themselves properly in dealing with the people during social function, this is true in?', 'social graces', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:21:32', '2021-01-21 16:21:32'),
(1467, 30, 1, 'Being the law making body, it is one of the vital government institutions than can support the PNP. This is', 'Congress', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:22:08', '2021-01-21 16:22:08'),
(1468, 32, 1, 'In order to check for Chvostek’s sign, the nurse will:', 'Spasm of the facial muscles is an indicator of low serum calcium levels.', 'easy', 30, '2021-01-21 16:22:54', '2021-01-21 16:22:54'),
